00:12:54,370 --> 00:12:59,190
Oh, no! Minister Oven!
Straw Hat Luffy is going to escape town!

186
00:12:59,190 --> 00:13:01,420
Escape town?!

187
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:12,120
Goodbye, failure!

188
00:13:15,540 --> 00:13:18,680
Snack! Brownie! Joconde!

189
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:21,090
Shoot them down at the harbor!

190
00:13:21,090 --> 00:13:23,090
They're coming toward you!

191
00:13:23,090 --> 00:13:25,550
Hey! Isn't someone talking to us
through the transponder snail?!

192
00:13:30,210 --> 00:13:32,700
I think I can make it!

193
00:13:32,700 --> 00:13:36,870
Don't let him go any further!
Prepare tear gas canisters!

194
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:41,450
We should just take away his ability to fly!

195
00:13:53,150 --> 00:13:54,260
What's the matter?!

196
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:56,010
Stay with us!

197
00:13:56,010 --> 00:13:58,070
Hey! Hey!

198
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,860
Germa!

199
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:07,240
Those who hurt my little brother...

200
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:10,400
I won't forgive them!

201
00:14:12,150 --> 00:14:15,740
If I can... escape...

202
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:19,740
here in the East Blue...

203
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:26,310
I'll never...

204
00:14:26,310 --> 00:14:29,180
have to see...

205
00:14:29,180 --> 00:14:31,690
Father's face again, right?

206
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:41,930
Pink Hornet!

207
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:48,030
That's Straw Hat! Shoot!

208
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:55,530
You're really a high-maintenance brother.

209
00:14:57,960 --> 00:15:00,670
Don't ever let him go!

210
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:05,540
Sanji! You're a boy!
Stop crying already!

211
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:10,150
Listen! Don't ever come back here!

212
00:15:10,150 --> 00:15:10,930
Uh-huh!

213
00:15:19,410 --> 00:15:22,460
Run!

214
00:15:22,460 --> 00:15:24,010
Don't look back!

215
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:32,930
Sanji... My kid brother
and the kindest person in the world!

216
00:15:33,550 --> 00:15:34,560
Reiju!

217
00:15:35,980 --> 00:15:37,190
Goodbye!

218
00:15:57,150 --> 00:16:02,070
Straw Hat got off of the island!
Fleet, come in!

219
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:06,950
Hurry up, Sanji!

220
00:16:12,710 --> 00:16:14,550
It's Sanji!

221
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:16,510
Here he comes, everyone!

222
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:20,010
Sanji is carrying Luffy!

223
00:16:22,010 --> 00:16:23,750
Yay!

224
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:25,670
I knew Sanji could do it!

225
00:16:25,670 --> 00:16:26,980
Luffy!

226
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:33,680
I can see it now, Luffy!
It's the Sunny !

227
00:16:34,210 --> 00:16:37,280
Is dinner ready yet, Sanji?

228
00:16:40,060 --> 00:16:43,920
Mont d'Or's Tactical Operations Center
Sweet City, Whole Cake Island

229
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:46,000
Brother Peros!

230
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:48,850
Please respond! How's Mama doing?!

231
00:16:48,850 --> 00:16:50,840
And what about Bege?! And the cake?!

232
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:55,600
Depending on what you say, things might get even crazier on Cacao Island, Brother Peros!

233
00:16:56,220 --> 00:16:59,980
Big Mom's Forces, At Sea

234
00:16:57,050 --> 00:16:59,980
Please respond, Big Bro Peros!

235
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:02,290
Yeah, I know!

236
00:17:04,990 --> 00:17:08,780
I still have my eyes
on Mama, Bege, and the others!

237
00:17:08,780 --> 00:17:11,720
Huh? What's wrong, Brother Peros?!

238
00:17:15,580 --> 00:17:18,580
Big Brother Mont d'Or! This is Bavarois!

239
00:17:18,580 --> 00:17:24,790
Brother Peros left his wound untreated for too long,
so he's losing his strength!

240
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:26,020
What?!

241
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:29,040
Now isn't the time to
worry about that... lick!

242
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:30,170
Give me that!

243
00:17:32,450 --> 00:17:38,270
We’re near Puffs Island now! It’s pandemonium here, too!

244
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:42,790
Chiffon and Bege finally dropped off the cake!

245
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:47,140
The cake is on Puffs Island! Lick!

246
00:17:47,140 --> 00:17:50,890
In just a few minutes, this'll all be over!

247
00:17:51,610 --> 00:17:56,090
Even if that cake is laced
with deadly poison,

248
00:17:56,090 --> 00:17:58,920
there's no way for us to stop her anymore!

249
00:18:02,330 --> 00:18:06,570
There are three possible outcomes!

250
00:18:06,570 --> 00:18:07,940
First:

251
00:18:07,940 --> 00:18:10,280
By eating the poisoned cake,

252
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:13,240
Mama dies!

253
00:18:21,190 --> 00:18:22,330
Second:

254
00:18:22,330 --> 00:18:24,650
The poison won't affect Mama,

255
00:18:24,650 --> 00:18:26,670
but the cake will taste bad!

256
00:18:26,670 --> 00:18:27,710
Yuck!

257
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:33,550
In that case, it won't quell her hunger,
and she'll continue destroying the country!

258
00:18:33,550 --> 00:18:35,510
And third:

259
00:18:35,510 --> 00:18:39,030
The poison in the cake doesn't affect her
and it tastes good!

260
00:18:39,030 --> 00:18:43,360
It would take a miracle,
but it's the only way we can survive!

261
00:18:43,360 --> 00:18:45,730
Prepare yourselves!

262
00:18:45,730 --> 00:18:50,250
The taste of that cake will decide our fates!

263
00:18:52,670 --> 00:18:55,160
This is the worst situation ever-soir !

264
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:58,120
Inform the entire country!

265
00:18:58,120 --> 00:18:59,750
They already know.

266
00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:02,400
Mama is out of control right now...

267
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:05,350
I heard that Nuts Island
was completely devastated.

268
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:06,040
What?!

269
00:19:06,040 --> 00:19:09,050
What's gonna happen to Totto Land?

270
00:19:09,050 --> 00:19:13,490
Our lives are on the line
with this cake-bon !

271
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:18,220
Hey! Where did Morgans and Stussy go?!

272
00:19:18,220 --> 00:19:20,480
They left the island a while ago...

273
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,770
What?!

274
00:19:21,770 --> 00:19:23,420
Capture them!

275
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:28,610
If the worst result happens,
the news will leak to the outside world!

276
00:19:28,610 --> 00:19:29,490
Yes, sir!

277
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:36,200
At the cost of all else,
that journalist must not leave the country!

278
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:38,950
There's no telling what he could publish...

279
00:19:38,950 --> 00:19:42,870
This island is doomed!
Let's get out of here!

280
00:19:42,870 --> 00:19:47,210
Mama's gonna destroy it just like Nuts Island!

281
00:19:43,210 --> 00:19:47,210
Fluffy Town, Puffs Island

282
00:19:47,210 --> 00:19:51,920
Madam Chiffon was brainwashed
by the traitor, Bege!

283
00:19:55,550 --> 00:19:57,550
Chiffon! What are you saying?!

284
00:19:59,810 --> 00:20:04,980
I’m doing this because I believe in the cake Black Leg made.

285
00:20:05,490 --> 00:20:08,420
I don't know where he learned to cook...

286
00:20:08,420 --> 00:20:13,110
but his culinary skills surpass even those of the head chef!

287
00:20:16,990 --> 00:20:18,200
Vito! Gotti!

288
00:20:18,970 --> 00:20:22,590
You two go look for a ship to escape on!

289
00:20:22,590 --> 00:20:25,320
I'll bring Chiffon with me later!

290
00:20:25,320 --> 00:20:27,660
O-Okay-rero !

291
00:20:27,660 --> 00:20:28,990
Got it!

292
00:20:28,990 --> 00:20:31,950
We paid off our debt to the Straw Hats.

293
00:20:31,950 --> 00:20:34,330
We lost our precious ship.

294
00:20:34,330 --> 00:20:36,850
Those damn Straw Hats!

295
00:20:36,850 --> 00:20:40,420
They'd better not end up dead
after all we've done for them!

296
00:20:50,430 --> 00:20:52,890
Wedding...

297
00:21:00,320 --> 00:21:04,600
cake!

298
00:21:09,800 --> 00:21:13,290
Yay! They're back!

299
00:21:13,290 --> 00:21:14,600
Luffy!

300
00:21:14,600 --> 00:21:15,640
Sanji!

301
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:16,630
Luffy-san !

302
00:21:16,630 --> 00:21:18,480
Luffy!

303
00:21:21,050 --> 00:21:23,020
I'm glad that you're okay!

304
00:21:23,020 --> 00:21:25,760
I'm so happy! Really!

305
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:30,180
He's totally worn out...

306
00:21:31,270 --> 00:21:34,140
Well done! Luffy! Sanji!

307
00:21:34,140 --> 00:21:36,430
I was so worried, Luffy!

308
00:21:36,430 --> 00:21:38,600
Garchu!

309
00:21:40,750 --> 00:21:43,570
You guys kept me waiting so long!

310
00:21:43,570 --> 00:21:45,110
Yeah, right!

311
00:21:45,110 --> 00:21:48,280
Luffy... Did you beat Katakuri?

312
00:21:51,430 --> 00:21:52,410
Yeah!

313
00:21:52,410 --> 00:21:53,600
Wow!

314
00:21:53,600 --> 00:21:56,210
I'm so impressed, Luffy-san !

315
00:21:58,500 --> 00:21:59,420
He fell asleep?!

316
00:21:59,420 --> 00:22:01,890
His wounds are still fresh...

317
00:22:01,890 --> 00:22:06,980
Chopper-san, attend to his wounds!
He's losing too much blood, isn't he?!

318
00:22:06,980 --> 00:22:07,860
Yeah!

319
00:22:17,190 --> 00:22:20,250
Sanji, you too. You got shot!

320
00:22:21,570 --> 00:22:24,580
Oh, this is nothing.

321
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:33,980
Good! We're finally in range.

322
00:22:36,410 --> 00:22:39,360
We didn’t notice them catching up!

323
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:43,160
We haven't lost them yet!
Treat him as we sail away!

324
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,600
Uh-huh!

325
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:06,510
Fire!

326
00:23:19,650 --> 00:23:20,820
What the...?

327
00:23:27,350 --> 00:23:29,450
Germa's backing them up!

328
00:23:29,450 --> 00:23:31,370
Damn you, Judge!

329
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,660
Should we return fire?!

330
00:23:33,660 --> 00:23:35,690
No, ignore them!

331
00:23:35,690 --> 00:23:39,210
Germa is also fighting
the fleet at the harbor!

332
00:23:39,210 --> 00:23:41,260
Aim at Straw Hat's ship!

333
00:23:41,260 --> 00:23:42,000
Yes, ma'am!

334
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:14,660
Why do you care so much
about him, Straw Hat Luffy?!

335
00:24:16,580 --> 00:24:19,960
This is Emperor Big Mom's territory!

336
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:23,040
You're in a place where escape
is impossible once you enter!

337
00:24:23,040 --> 00:24:27,510
And yet, you risked your life
just to take back one person?!

338
00:24:27,510 --> 00:24:31,320
Sanji is Germa's failure!

339
00:24:32,860 --> 00:24:35,920
He can't use his skin as a shield...

340
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:43,120
He cooks because he doesn't
have a shred of royal pride!

341
00:24:44,210 --> 00:24:45,420
Uh-huh...

342
00:24:46,040 --> 00:24:48,840
He's an idiot with a soft spot...

343
00:24:49,880 --> 00:24:56,180
and a soft mind that makes him put his life on the line for the weak!

344
00:24:56,180 --> 00:25:00,930
He is truly unfit to be a soldier!

345
00:25:00,930 --> 00:25:03,410
That's all he is!

346
00:25:09,100 --> 00:25:11,810
Goodbye! Thank you for your help!

347
00:25:12,560 --> 00:25:14,850
Why don't you answer me?!

348
00:25:15,310 --> 00:25:17,480
Straw Hat!

349
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:23,320
I'm surprised. Why did he suddenly start listing
all the good things about you?

350
00:25:23,320 --> 00:25:27,110
What?! He didn't mean it that way!

351
00:25:27,110 --> 00:25:28,210
What?!

352
00:25:31,470 --> 00:25:33,870
You guys are the best!

353
00:25:40,630 --> 00:25:42,190
Nami! Look ahead!

354
00:25:42,190 --> 00:25:43,570
What?

355
00:25:43,570 --> 00:25:45,690
No! This is terrible!

356
00:25:47,040 --> 00:25:50,630
Jinbe! There's a massive fleet
right in front of us!

357
00:25:50,630 --> 00:25:52,650
When did they get here?!

358
00:25:53,620 --> 00:25:55,530
Looks like they finally noticed...

359
00:25:56,990 --> 00:25:58,410
It's an entire armada!

360
00:25:58,410 --> 00:26:01,280
