472
00:26:08,970 --> 00:26:11,920
We're already in their firing range!

473
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:13,050
How?!

474
00:26:14,170 --> 00:26:15,480
That's right!

475
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:18,640
We're coming from both the
front and back, rabbit!

476
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,990
Carrot-chan !

477
00:26:19,990 --> 00:26:23,680
In front of you, a fleet...
behind you, a jinni!

478
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:24,720
Jinni-uinely...

479
00:26:25,520 --> 00:26:27,480
Enraged Cleave!

480
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:28,810
Black Leg?!

481
00:26:29,330 --> 00:26:30,230
Sanji!

482
00:26:32,760 --> 00:26:34,440
He's huge!

483
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:41,620
You've finally entered the range of my ability!

484
00:26:41,620 --> 00:26:45,620
Now it looks like we're bullying them.

485
00:26:47,910 --> 00:26:50,330
How did they close in so quickly?!

486
00:26:50,330 --> 00:26:53,090
Look closely at the ships in front of us!

487
00:26:57,300 --> 00:27:00,240
They're all paddle ships!

488
00:27:01,590 --> 00:27:02,490
No way!

489
00:27:02,490 --> 00:27:04,470
There's no way we can escape!

490
00:27:04,470 --> 00:27:09,690
I guess this is the end! We were barely able to make it this far, but...

491
00:27:09,690 --> 00:27:11,660
Crush them!

492
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:20,100
What's going on?!

493
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:27,350
The surface of the sea is swelling up...

494
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:34,160
I won't forgive anyone who...

495
00:27:35,560 --> 00:27:40,600
gives the boss any trouble!

496
00:27:45,210 --> 00:27:46,960
What?!

497
00:27:46,960 --> 00:27:50,590
That guy... he was a member
of Hody's crew on Fishman Island...

498
00:27:50,590 --> 00:27:52,520
Wadatsumi!

499
00:27:53,840 --> 00:27:54,680
What?

500
00:27:55,050 --> 00:27:55,970
No way!

501
00:27:55,970 --> 00:27:57,930
Jinbe!

502
00:28:02,860 --> 00:28:04,320
You guys!

503
00:28:08,990 --> 00:28:13,600
We came to see you off, Captain Jinbe!

504
00:28:13,600 --> 00:28:16,370
Ah, that's "former"! Former Captain!

505
00:28:23,080 --> 00:28:28,840
Until you get out of Big Mom’s territory, we’re still your crew… all right?!

506
00:28:30,360 --> 00:28:32,170
I got it!

507
00:28:33,630 --> 00:28:36,130
Go away!

508
00:28:36,130 --> 00:28:37,920
So cool!

509
00:28:40,260 --> 00:28:42,120
W-What the...?!

510
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:43,810
It's flooded!

511
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:48,350
Someone punched holes in the bottom?!

512
00:28:49,380 --> 00:28:51,480
There are fishmen in the water!

513
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:53,690
How are they so sneaky?!

514
00:28:53,690 --> 00:28:56,480
Come out, you damn fishmen!

515
00:29:03,550 --> 00:29:05,620
You bastards!

516
00:29:09,210 --> 00:29:10,250
Damn!

517
00:29:10,250 --> 00:29:12,380
I won't let the Straw Hats get away!

518
00:29:14,340 --> 00:29:16,750
Jinni!

519
00:29:18,630 --> 00:29:20,050
Ocean Current...

520
00:29:20,110 --> 00:29:23,140
Shoulder Throw!

521
00:29:43,030 --> 00:29:43,990
Look!

522
00:29:47,380 --> 00:29:49,560
A path opened on the sea!

523
00:30:02,330 --> 00:30:05,840
Push forward while we
hold them off, Captain Jinbe!

524
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:10,260
We won't let you
harm the Straw Hats' ship!

525
00:30:16,140 --> 00:30:18,100
Thank you!

526
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:21,130
Why didn't I notice?

527
00:30:21,130 --> 00:30:26,980
They disabled the enemy's
territorial sea slugs for us, too.

528
00:30:26,980 --> 00:30:30,780
They ended up helping me to the very end.

529
00:30:30,780 --> 00:30:34,620
As expected of Jinbe's crew!

530
00:30:34,620 --> 00:30:36,270
Yeah!

531
00:30:36,270 --> 00:30:38,170
Thanks...

532
00:30:38,170 --> 00:30:40,120
you guys!

533
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:44,960
Take care of Jinbe for us, Straw Hat!

534
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:46,360
Okay!

535
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:51,670
Fire!

536
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:57,130
Merge!

537
00:31:11,230 --> 00:31:15,440
Minister Oven,
shouldn't you be on Cacao Island?!

538
00:31:16,360 --> 00:31:20,650
I left Germa to Brûlée!

539
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:24,670
These are heavy-metal
composite bullets that can easily

540
00:31:24,670 --> 00:31:27,740
punch holes through
Germa's raid suits!

541
00:31:27,740 --> 00:31:30,500
Go teach them a lesson!

542
00:31:30,500 --> 00:31:31,290
Yes, ma'am!

543
00:31:43,340 --> 00:31:45,300
It's that guy again!

544
00:31:48,220 --> 00:31:51,100
Straw Hat!

545
00:31:54,940 --> 00:31:58,860
Since you brought down Katakuri,
you're the last person...

546
00:31:58,860 --> 00:32:00,820
I'd ever let leave alive!

547
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:11,960
What's gonna happen?

548
00:32:20,940 --> 00:32:24,270
Don't worry. It's gonna be alright!

549
00:32:24,270 --> 00:32:26,510
The man who baked it....

550
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:28,350
is a true chef!

551
00:32:29,820 --> 00:32:33,520
Wait, Black Leg!
Won’t that method take all night?

552
00:32:33,520 --> 00:32:35,430
Taking this time is vital.

553
00:32:35,430 --> 00:32:37,100
But we don't have time!

554
00:32:37,100 --> 00:32:38,710
I'll do it in two hours!

555
00:32:38,710 --> 00:32:40,540
You're kidding!

556
00:32:41,990 --> 00:32:46,180
Why are you smiling?!
Get serious, Black Leg!

557
00:32:47,020 --> 00:32:51,860
Your ship and our country are at stake!

558
00:32:52,950 --> 00:32:54,270
I'm sorry...

559
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:57,020
I just couldn't help thinking about...

560
00:32:57,020 --> 00:33:00,490
Big Mom's delighted face
as she calls this cake "delicious."

561
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:02,470
How lovely!

562
00:33:02,470 --> 00:33:03,830
Her delighted face?!

563
00:33:03,830 --> 00:33:06,760
Don't you realize that your life is in danger?

564
00:33:16,930 --> 00:33:18,320
Mama!

565
00:33:21,900 --> 00:33:24,040
Did the poison kill her?!

566
00:33:34,920 --> 00:33:40,370
It's so delicious...
that I could die right now!

567
00:33:40,370 --> 00:33:43,120
The sweetness is unbelievable!

568
00:33:46,460 --> 00:33:50,840
This is it!

569
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:55,760
The wedding cake!

570
00:33:58,200 --> 00:33:59,910
She stopped...

571
00:33:59,910 --> 00:34:01,300
What about the poison?!

572
00:34:01,300 --> 00:34:06,440
I'm sure it was in there!
It just didn't work! That's our Mama!

573
00:34:10,250 --> 00:34:12,610
Black Leg!

574
00:34:12,610 --> 00:34:15,190
That's the look that you wished to see!

575
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:19,730
♪ It's superb! This sweetness! ♪

576
00:34:19,730 --> 00:34:23,300
♪ I know I've tasted it somewhere! ♪

577
00:34:23,300 --> 00:34:29,100
It's delicious!

578
00:34:32,710 --> 00:34:36,230
To all islands of Totto Land...

579
00:34:36,230 --> 00:34:40,130
the damage will spread no further!

580
00:34:47,220 --> 00:34:51,300
Because of the efforts of the
Charlotte family's 35th daughter, Pudding,

581
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:54,180
Mama's ravenous rampage has been quelled!

582
00:34:54,180 --> 00:34:59,080
Thank goodness! I thought this island would be next,
since we're so close to Cacao Island!

583
00:34:59,080 --> 00:35:01,010
It was scary!

584
00:35:01,010 --> 00:35:02,610
We're okay now!

585
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:05,040
Thank you, Bege!

586
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:23,230
By using Madam Chiffon, who betrayed the country,
Madam Pudding saved Totto Land!

587
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:24,990
No one else could do it!

588
00:35:24,990 --> 00:35:27,520
Thank you, Madam Pudding!

589
00:35:27,520 --> 00:35:30,370
That's our Madam Pudding!

590
00:35:30,370 --> 00:35:31,780
No...

591
00:35:32,270 --> 00:35:33,890
It wasn't me.

592
00:35:41,120 --> 00:35:42,940
Bring it on!

593
00:35:51,180 --> 00:35:54,390
Sparking Figure!

594
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:04,610
Hot Sea Hell!

595
00:36:17,170 --> 00:36:20,210
Everyone, swim deeper into the sea!

596
00:36:20,210 --> 00:36:23,590
It's too hot! I can't get near him!

597
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:27,080
There is no protection for you guys!

598
00:36:27,080 --> 00:36:29,470
And you have nowhere to run!

599
00:36:33,470 --> 00:36:34,470
Dammit!

600
00:36:34,470 --> 00:36:37,100
What should we do, Luffy?!

601
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:45,000
Let's...

602
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:47,790
advance!

603
00:36:51,180 --> 00:36:55,120
The Queen Mama Chanter will be
arriving at Cacao Island soon.

604
00:36:59,170 --> 00:37:03,050
Alright! Just in time!

605
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:12,390
Fluffy!

606
00:37:12,890 --> 00:37:14,560
Munch!

607
00:37:14,560 --> 00:37:16,350
Gulp!

608
00:37:18,980 --> 00:37:19,940
♪ Fluffy! ♪

609
00:37:19,940 --> 00:37:20,980
♪ Munch! ♪

610
00:37:20,980 --> 00:37:21,900
♪ Gulp! ♪

611
00:37:23,020 --> 00:37:23,820
♪ Fluffy! ♪

612
00:37:23,820 --> 00:37:24,940
♪ Munch! ♪

613
00:37:24,940 --> 00:37:25,900
♪ Gulp! ♪

614
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,350
♪ What... ♪

615
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:30,170
♪ is this?! ♪

616
00:37:30,870 --> 00:37:34,790
♪ Dreamy... taste? ♪

617
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:34,790
♪ Flower! Flower! ♪

618
00:37:34,790 --> 00:37:38,970
♪ It's something that's beyond my wildest dreams! ♪

619
00:37:38,970 --> 00:37:42,970
♪ I can't even find the words to describe it! ♪

620
00:37:42,970 --> 00:37:44,890
♪ What? What? ♪

621
00:37:44,890 --> 00:37:46,930
♪ What's this flavor? ♪

622
00:37:46,930 --> 00:37:50,940
♪ It's making rotten puppies start dancing! ♪

623
00:37:50,940 --> 00:37:53,910
♪ The flavor is concentrated like... ♪

624
00:37:53,910 --> 00:37:59,880
♪ ...a pet cemetery! ♪

625
00:38:10,870 --> 00:38:13,010
♪ It's sweet! ♪

626
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,850
♪ It's sweet... ♪

627
00:38:13,010 --> 00:38:15,050
♪ It's milky! ♪

628
00:38:13,870 --> 00:38:15,890
♪ It's milky... ♪

629
00:38:15,050 --> 00:38:21,180
♪ It's very rich and... ♪

630
00:38:17,010 --> 00:38:21,180
♪ It's very rich and... ♪

631
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:24,980
♪ risky! ♪

632
00:38:31,060 --> 00:38:36,980
♪ Look! Yes, it's a big fuss! ♪

633
00:38:35,020 --> 00:38:36,980
♪ Ship! Ship! ♪

634
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:41,030
♪ It's like when you throw a bomb... ♪

635
00:38:41,030 --> 00:38:46,070
♪ into an amusement park! ♪

636
00:38:49,990 --> 00:38:52,070
♪ Like your stomach is having... ♪

637
00:38:52,070 --> 00:38:57,130
♪ ...a big ceremony! ♪

638
00:39:03,220 --> 00:39:06,760
♪ Hey, Mother... ♪

639
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:15,940
♪ can you taste this overflowing happy sweetness? ♪

640
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:18,980
"Happy birthday, Linlin"

641
00:39:18,980 --> 00:39:20,270
Oh, yeah!

642
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:24,710
♪ It's the flavor of happiness... ♪

643
00:39:20,520 --> 00:39:32,790
"Happy birthday, Linlin"

644
00:39:24,710 --> 00:39:29,990
♪ from back then! ♪

645
00:39:29,990 --> 00:39:32,790
Happy birthday,

646
00:39:32,790 --> 00:39:35,080
Linlin!

647
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:45,010
♪ Let's eat again together someday! ♪

648
00:39:45,010 --> 00:39:46,870
♪ It's sweet! ♪

649
00:39:45,930 --> 00:39:48,160
♪ It's sweet... ♪

650
00:39:46,870 --> 00:39:48,970
♪ It's milky! ♪

651
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:50,530
♪ It's milky... ♪

652
00:39:48,970 --> 00:39:56,520
♪ It's very rich and... ♪

653
00:39:51,140 --> 00:39:56,520
♪ It's very rich and... ♪

654
00:39:56,660 --> 00:40:00,020
♪ risky! ♪

655
00:40:13,240 --> 00:40:17,040
Hey, Mother, do you think...

656
00:40:17,040 --> 00:40:19,120
I can do this?

657
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:25,210
♪ Everyone's happy! ♪

658
00:40:25,210 --> 00:40:28,940
♪ It's a peaceful utopia! ♪

659
00:40:28,940 --> 00:40:37,130
♪ It doesn't discriminate by race! ♪

660
00:40:37,130 --> 00:40:44,430
♪ If you try to leave, I'll kill you, though... ♪

661
00:40:44,430 --> 00:40:48,910
♪ It's a devilish contract! ♪

662
00:40:48,910 --> 00:40:53,070
♪ The peaceful Totto Land! ♪

663
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:56,820
♪ We're all family! ♪

664
00:40:56,820 --> 00:41:01,840
♪ The gentle queen... ♪

665
00:41:02,620 --> 00:41:03,950
♪ Big Mom! ♪

666
00:41:16,930 --> 00:41:19,040
♪ It was delicious! ♪

667
00:41:19,040 --> 00:41:22,090
♪ Thank you for the meal... ♪
